  Barbarella, space bimbo, is a futuristic girl from 41st-century Earth who is called on to retrieve Duran-Duran, a noted scientist, from the evil planet of SoGo. On her perilous (and quite sexy) journey she teams with blind angel Pygar (John Phillip Law), and battles the Black Queen (Anita Pallenberg) and survives various sexual torture devices. Barbarella is full of vintage 60's retro influence. A Spaceship, with wall-to-wall shag carpeting, traveling through a Lava Lamp. And who can forget Jane Fonda's zero gravity striptease.
